Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102165,103291}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103374,105001}Good morning, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:45.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105084,105918}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106252,108504}Good morning. It's getting\Nso cold these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108630,111174}Of course it is.\NChristmas is almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:54.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111466,114802}Christmas. Wouldn't it be nice\Nif it snowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:55.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114927,115970}It certainly would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:59.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116012,119682}Has anybody noticed how quiet\Nthe class has gotten lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122935,125104}And the reason is\Nright over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125396,126606}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126773,130485}He hasn't received any notes\Nfrom St. Tail lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130777,132362}And that's why\Nhe's been down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132862,136574}I understand how he feels.\NHe misses the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:21.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137367,141245}Is that why he's so gloomy? How silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142330,144540}Cheer up, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146292,149420}Oh. It's only you, Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149545,150713}How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:33.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151130,153091}So what if St. Tail doesn't appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153174,154759}It only proves\Nthe world is at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154801,156052}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156886,159180}How can you jabber so much\Nfirst thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159889,162016}That's why I can't stand\Nthe girls in this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:43.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162350,163726}What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163768,167730}You're all nosy, loud-mouthed\Nand unfeminine on top of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170441,172819}Okay, then tell me\Nwhat's your ideal girl like, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173069,174320}Come on, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174654,176906}It's not you, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:59.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177115,179992}There's no such thing\Nas the perfect girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:03.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180368,183121}Yes, there is!\NTake St. Tail, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:10.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186541,190545}What's wrong with you?\NIt's always St. Tail, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192839,193965}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198136,199387}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200012,203683}You moron!\NI hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:30.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206227,210106}I'm St. Tail.\NAnd if I'm her, then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:41.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216696,221659}Surprise!\NThe Large Lizard Santa Claus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233963,238885}Mayu, isn't it?\NThere's no one here but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238968,240636}You can tell me\Nyour problem now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241179,245683}Sister, Goh stole Tama from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,246851}Goh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246976,250563}He's in my class\Nand he's so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250813,252565}I'm not even bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:14.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252648,254942}but he kicks my blocks\Nand hits me with the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255401,257612}And he's the one\Nwho stole your pet, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258529,259322}Uh huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260406,262283}Did you tell your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:29.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263618,269373}But Mama hates animals.\NShe said he should keep Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269457,270416}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271876,273628}I really love Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:38.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273669,278049}I understand. Don't cry.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278424,279550}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:44.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283513,284931}And that's the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285181,288893}Goh is really Gohta Ogasawara.\NHe's five years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289185,291521}And he lives on the hill\Non the outskirts of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291896,293773}And what does Tama look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294357,297735}She's black in color and\Nhas a ribbon around her neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298027,299904}I think she'll be easy to spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300363,303908}Alright. I guess I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304408,307203}Wait, what about a\Nnote to Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307662,310289}Forget it.\NWho cares about that promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:13.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310706,313751}That means\Nyou'll be breaking the promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:15.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314377,315670}I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317046,318339}Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319215,321926}He only thinks of St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:24.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321968,324720}I'm not sending another\Nnote to that guy. Not ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331102,334021}The bully's room\Nshould be underneath me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350329,351873}Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355334,357295}So you're the little meany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358004,361549}You'd better start\Nthinking about how girls feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:05.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362216,365094}Or you'll end up like\Na certain blockhead I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:14.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369849,374478}Phew. Gee, I almost forgot.\NNow, where's that Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:23.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379358,383529}Here Tama... Oh, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398085,401464}Black in color,\Nwith a ribbon. It can't be, can it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:46.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402173,406677}TAMA\NAre you Tama? I thought you'd\Nbe a cute little black cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414936,418147}What'll I do?\NI'm too scared to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418522,420858}Which means I can't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421400,422735}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422777,424779}My reputation is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:24.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441295,444131}Tama, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455142,456143}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457520,460815}I'll call it quits for tonight.\NI've got to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464485,466362}Detective Asuka, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468364,469281}After her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.49,0:07:52.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469490,472159}It's St. Tail! After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474078,475121}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485965,487800}We've got her cornered now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488259,489510}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497810,499520}I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503315,504442}Oh, damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:27.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506527,507319}Detective Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:29.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508154,509113}Don't hang on to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509155,510406}I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510489,511282}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511323,515244}-Don't do that, sir!\N-Help, I'm sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516912,519623}St. Tail appears!\NBut what is her target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519874,521292}The mystery thickens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523210,525755}Detective Asuka\Nmisses the arrest by an inch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526505,529216}It's been pretty long\Nsince St. Tail's last caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529383,533179}I heard your Dad came close\Nto capturing her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533429,534847}Isn't that right, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535097,538684}Shut up!\NShe never sent me a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538934,540436}That's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,542730}Who does she think\Nshe's dealing with, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542980,544648}Calm down, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545316,547526}I was waiting for a note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548027,550654}Why'd she do it\Nwithout letting me know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:13.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551072,553407}What'll I do?\NIt's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553991,558954}Cheer up. I'm sure she just\Nforgot her promise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559538,563042}She's not like that!\NShe'd never break her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563125,565294}Then I'm sure she has\Na very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:26.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565336,566837}Just mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567046,570883}I don't want to hear your ideas\Nabout St. Tail's motives!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571342,575971}What?! You'll never capture St. Tail,\Nnot in a million years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576097,578766}Oh, be quiet!\NYou don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578891,579809}Oh, yes I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579850,580935}Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582978,585523}Yes, I do!\NBecause I'm St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585856,586899}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587775,590027}Huh?\NWhat was that about St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590361,591278}Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604708,607753}Oh, brother,\NI can't believe I said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609922,613843}Ruby, do you think\NAsuka caught what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617429,619390}SEIKA NEWS STATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:25.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621809,625146}Good evening.\NThis is the Seika News Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625729,629150}Our first story this evening features\Nthe city's Christmas Eve festivities...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629191,631110}Hey, you!\NHow'd you get in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631193,632236}You shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634530,636824}Mama, come look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638033,639618}What is it, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:44.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640786,644415}Isn't that Meimi's classmate on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644456,645207}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645249,648085}Give me a break!\NI'll make it quick!\NSee? It's that smart kid.\NThe mayor's pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648210,650713}That's not possible right now!\NYou're right.\NI wonder what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651088,652089}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652631,653382}Grump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653841,654675}Ow! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654925,656135}Hey! Hey! That's my mic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656218,657178}What is it, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657219,658012}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658637,661640}I have a message for St. Tail!\NMeet me tonight at Park A!\NLook, isn't that boy in your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661640,662892}I have a message for St. Tail!\NMeet me tonight at Park A!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663225,665269}I'll be waiting alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668230,669648}I'm doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670274,673027}If you don't come,\NI'll reveal your identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673068,674195}...to the entire city!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676697,679825}There's no escaping those eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680743,683120}Quick! Cut the cameras! Cut!\NYou hear me?!\NI'll repeat it once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:25.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683245,685039}Please Stand By\NSEIKA TV
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685164,688876}St. Tail, eh?\NI'll bet she's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689293,691170}Just like when you were younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:34.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691378,694298}Hey, I'm still beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696050,697509}Meimi, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697801,700429}Meimi? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:58.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714401,718113}You mustn't go. It's a bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718364,720908}It might be one\Nof Asuka Jr's. tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:07.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722034,727414}You're right.\NDo you think I'm crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729291,732628}If I'm going to be caught,\NI have this funny feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732670,735005}it'd be better if Asuka\Nwas the one to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735589,736840}Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:19.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737258,739551}Do you think\NI shouldn't go, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742972,745599}It wouldn't do any good\Nto stop you, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746267,748018}But listen, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:31.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748310,751397}You must never reveal your\Nidentity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751689,755025}You must take him by surprise\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755109,755943}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756026,760030}We don't know how much\Nhe really knows, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:45.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761657,765911}Besides, you have\Na job to do tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765953,766704}I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766829,768330}Yes, for Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768872,772001}Oh, that's right.\NI haven't gotten Tama back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:57.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772584,777548}Poor Mayu. She's been waiting\Nanxiously for Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:01.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777673,781135}You're right. But why\Ndoes it have to be tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781885,785347}The truth is,\NMayu and her family are moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785347,787516}to another city far from here\Ntomorrow, Christmas Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787683,789143}She's moving away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794231,796483}Mayu, just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:22.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798527,802740}That's why tonight\Nis the last chance you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805159,806660}Alright, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806910,809997}Let's give her an\Nunforgettable Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810456,811415}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:36.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812958,816962}Meimi, when the time comes that\Nyou're captured, we'll go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825095,828599}Lord, forgive me\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833687,834563}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837441,838233}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840486,842446}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857878,861465}May the blessings\Nof God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872476,875187}Maybe she wasn't watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:47.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881235,887616}Snow... It's going to be a white\NChristmas. Brr... it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893956,895916}Well, I guess\Nshe's not going to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916478,920065}What's that?\NSt. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924820,928615}You must take him by surprise,\Nas you've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931243,933912}I don't know what good it'll do but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937124,940419}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945674,947009}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:51.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948969,951472}Will you stop?\NI've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954600,957436}Why do you think\NI left that cell phone over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958812,962774}Listen! I'm not leaving here,\Nso you can just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964109,965277}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965486,969865}Yes! But you said\Nyou'd reveal my identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970073,971074}It was a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972242,974786}Oh, brother.\NHe doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974953,977664}Never mind that.\NWhy didn't you send me a note?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978207,979458}How do I explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979791,982753}Is that why you called me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:25.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983170,985631}This is very important,\Nso listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986131,987382}You know what it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987424,989134}if you don't let me know\Nwhere you're going to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989593,991720}It means I won't be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:37.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992554,997267}And that means... um... er...\Nlet's put it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998894,1001396}What'll happen if\Nsomebody else captures you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002940,1004149}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004525,1007152}Oh... what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:48.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007361,1008362}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009571,1010822}I'm coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:51.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010989,1011865}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015244,1016745}Forgive me, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017996,1021458}You must never reveal\Nyour identity to him on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022584,1024294}But... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027881,1030759}Darn, the glass is\Nso fogged up, I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036640,1037766}St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044606,1045691}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047234,1049444}Uh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050153,1051280}My promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:38.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053115,1058453}I'm sorry I broke my promise.\NI'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058912,1059913}Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061373,1062332}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063917,1064960}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066003,1067045}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068171,1070382}I don't want you to\Ngive up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071758,1073343}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:18:00.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074970,1080017}St. Tail! Don't get caught\Nuntil I catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080851,1081852}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083061,1085897}It's a promise!\NDon't you forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089234,1090110}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107002,1109004}"I am going to\Nthe Ogasawara residence..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:32.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109046,1112007}"this evening to take\Ntheir pet, Tama - St. Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:36.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113008,1116470}Tonight?!\NI don't have much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117846,1119097}Darn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:44.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121391,1124269}I'm sorry,\Nbut tonight's the only night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124978,1126521}Hey! Tama's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128982,1131068}"Don't be mean to little girls!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:59.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138325,1139534}Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:04.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140827,1144706}What's that?!\NSt. Tail has shown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145332,1148710}Daddy, Mommy, wake up -\Nyou gotta see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149086,1150754}Santa is flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151171,1152339}Santa is flying in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152381,1153924}You must be dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156426,1157511}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161765,1163183}Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164643,1165936}It's Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173443,1176113}Wow! Presents from Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187582,1189501}Police vehicle coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189751,1194631}Clear the street!\NI repeat, clear the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195549,1197884}Darn... she got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200303,1203724}Mayu, forget about Tama and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:12.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209980,1212399}It's Tama! Tama's come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215318,1216903}Tama, oh Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219740,1222743}I guess we have no choice but\Nto take Tama with us, right, Mayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223326,1224077}Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:24.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224119,1224870}Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234504,1235672}St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235839,1238508}I'll get you\Nfor sure next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:41.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240218,1241845}Merry Christmas!
